title: Who Got Help, Who Didn't, and Who Will Pay Off Come September | The Ringer NFL Show (Ep. 246)
description:
The Ringer's Kevin Clark and Danny Kelly hook up to look at which teams made the most impressive moves during free agency (02:15), which teams seem to be lost and without a plan (25:15), and which signings will be the most impactful once the season starts (41:45).
Read our NFL free-agency coverage here: https://www.theringer.com/nfl
